ihaz's Scout Custom Upgrade List

At the time of writing this, these weapons were seen in..
• Rottenburg - Marathon (Easy Adv)

The goal of this list is to be as honest and objective as possible.

Notes:
While this mission is relatively easy, I do think at least it attempted to try to be unique.
Most of the custom upgrades were also quite creative.

