Scout
//===============
Primary
    2. Backscatter
	 • Unstable Overclock: Cloaker Tactics // On Kill: 4 seconds of cloak +Crits from behind -46% accurate -25% reload speed -20% firing speed
-- Potentially strong sidegrade, if not for the slow reload and BAD accuracy.
    --
      100% critical hits from behind
      On Kill: 4s of Invisibility
      Mini-crits targets when fired at their back from close range

      -34% clip size
      No random critical hits
      66% less accurate
      -25% slower reload time
      -25% slower firing speed

    4. Force-a-Nature
	 •  Unstable Overclock: Explosive Rounds // -100% firing speed -10% damage -No special knockback
-- FAN if it was good. Which is still a low bar compared to Stock and Soda Popper.
      +50% faster firing speed
      +90% reduced self damage
      +80% increase in self push force taken
      (HIDDEN) Bullets explodes on impact
      (HIDDEN) This weapon emits ("rd_robot_explosion_smoke_linger") particles when explodes

      -20% damage penalty
      -90% bullets per shot
      -66% clip size
      -100% slower firing speed
      No Random Crits
  
      This weapon reloads its entire clip at once

    5. Shortstop
	 •  Unstable Overclock: Swarm Missiles // Tap to fire a barrage of weak missiles +75% ammo capacity +50% firing speed +50% clip size -70% blast radius
-- Kind of underwhelming compared to the base shortstop. Similar to airstrike in terms of scaling.
-- Stat bloat I would reckon.
    --
      +115% damage bonus
      +90% faster firing speed 
      +16% clip size
      +75% max ammo
      Alt-Fire: Deal 1 damage and shove someone!
      (HIDDEN) Attacks will fire mini-rockets instead
      (HIDDEN) Firing will empty the entire clip
      (HIDDEN, COMMENTED OUT) +40% more accurate

      -50% slower reload time
      -70% rocket explosion radius
      No random crits
      (HIDDEN, COMMENTED OUT) -60% less bullet per shot

      This weapon reloads its entire clip at once.
      Increase in push force taken from damage and airblast

